    "body": "- [x] Broken example in #6601 does not hang anymore\r\n- [x] Codegen for the example in #5995 is still optimal, we just have more code now for computing the thread rank of the CG group\r\n- [x] Codegen of the above using a custom 1D thread block and `is_thread_block_group_v` optimal\r\n\r\nI pulled the core fix out into #6710, so it can ship on time for 3.2.\r\n\r\nFixes: #6601",
